'''索美塞特郡旗'''（'''flag of Somerset'''）是[[英國|英國]][[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[索美塞特郡|索美塞特郡]]的旗幟。在2006年至2009年，索美塞特郡舉辦了選出郡旗的活動 <ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20090409222349/http://www.somersetflag.com/main.html Somerset flag campaign site – Archived from 2009]</ref><ref name="abc">[http://abcounties.co.uk/counties/county-flags/county-flag-proposals?showall=1 Association of British Counties – County Flag proposals] {{webarchive|url=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20120902214429/http://abcounties.co.uk/counties/county-flags/county-flag-proposals?showall=1 |date=2012-09-02 }}</ref>，當地的報紙和BBC索美塞特郡也參加了這一活動<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/somerset/content/articles/2006/08/16/somerset_flag_feature.shtml |title=Does Somerset need its own flag? |access-date=2016-03-26 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126013537/http://www.bbc.co.uk/somerset/content/articles/2006/08/16/somerset_flag_feature.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年7月，現在的郡旗獲得通過。
